stored in execution context object

Regular function call - this keyword poinmts to global object
method call - this variable points to the object calling the method
this keyword i snot assigned a value until a function where it is defined is actually called.


REGULAR FUNCTION CALL ALWAYS , THIS IS ALWAYS POINTED TO WINDOW
THIS REFERS TO OBJECT THAT CALLED THE METHOD, this eill be assigned a value when object calls a method

